WEBVTT

00:01.335 --> 00:02.916
MR. BENNET:
Previously on Heroes.

00:03.045 --> 00:04.546
No matter what happens
in your world,

00:04.630 --> 00:06.086
you can always
come back to this one.

00:06.174 --> 00:07.334
I know.

00:07.425 --> 00:08.756
I'll find my way.

00:09.218 --> 00:10.253
Nice to meet you.

00:10.386 --> 00:11.501
PETER: Mom, this is Emma.

00:11.596 --> 00:13.427
She's going to kill
thousands of people.

00:13.556 --> 00:14.841
It will be a bloodbath.

00:14.932 --> 00:17.014
Tell me exactly
what you saw.

00:17.101 --> 00:18.932
You cannot save her.

00:19.020 --> 00:20.931
But someone else can.

00:22.565 --> 00:25.056
ANGELA: People think
that dreaming the future
is a gift.

00:25.151 --> 00:26.482
They’re wrong.

00:27.236 --> 00:28.567
SYLAR: I don't want
to be alone,

00:28.654 --> 00:30.485
and somehow
you're supposed
to help me.

00:30.615 --> 00:34.733
I can only imagine
what having
a bunch of excuses

00:34.827 --> 00:36.328
could do to
someone's humanity.

00:36.454 --> 00:37.694
In order to become
human again,

00:37.788 --> 00:40.780
he has to get rid
of all of his powers.

00:43.628 --> 00:44.959
Now was that so hard?

00:45.129 --> 00:46.869
I'm sorry. I'm Gabriel.
Friend of Matt's.

00:46.964 --> 00:48.500
I'm sorry.
He's not here
right now.

00:48.633 --> 00:50.169
Is there any way
that you could tell me
where he is?

00:50.259 --> 00:51.669
It's really important
that I speak with him.

00:52.011 --> 00:53.467
This is your fantasy.

00:53.596 --> 00:54.881
This isn't my life.

00:54.972 --> 00:56.678
Something wrong, sir?

00:57.016 --> 00:58.847
Yeah, something is wrong.

00:59.977 --> 01:01.308
(GRUNTING)

01:42.186 --> 01:44.097
lt's quiet.
Where is everyone?

01:44.272 --> 01:46.684
The carnival
is closed, Samuel.

01:49.986 --> 01:52.773
Everybody saw
what you did
to that town.

01:52.863 --> 01:54.364
They're afraid of me.

01:54.532 --> 01:56.363
Can you blame them?

01:57.368 --> 01:59.700
We finally have
a home here.

02:00.454 --> 02:03.036
A place to make a life.
It's what we wanted.

02:03.124 --> 02:05.035
It's what you told us
that you wanted.

02:05.126 --> 02:07.617
You don't trust me
anymore, do you?

02:07.712 --> 02:08.952
You haven't
for a long time.

02:09.046 --> 02:11.378
So show me why I should.

02:15.720 --> 02:18.211
Part of trust
is faith, Lydia.

02:18.848 --> 02:21.806
Must be very hard
for you to come by

02:21.892 --> 02:26.181
when you can steal a look
into someone's very soul
with just a touch.

02:26.522 --> 02:30.140
After all I've done for you,
for all of them,
I'm the villain?

02:30.234 --> 02:34.398
And you, you, it seems,
have become the empath
to replace Joseph.

02:35.823 --> 02:39.657
Everyone's looking to you now
for their voice, aren't they?

02:39.744 --> 02:42.076
What have you
been telling them?

02:44.040 --> 02:46.372
Nobody respects you anymore.

02:47.710 --> 02:49.917
And I'm gonna win it back.

02:51.589 --> 02:53.204
I love them.

02:54.091 --> 02:55.752
I need them.

03:00.222 --> 03:04.682
And I'll do
whatever I have to do
to prove my worth.

03:31.003 --> 03:32.618
(GIRL SCREAMING)

03:35.966 --> 03:38.799
Don't worry.
I'm here to save you.

03:40.805 --> 03:42.045
(GASPING)

04:00.825 --> 04:04.283
Hey, it's Peter Petrelli.
ls Emma Coolidge there?

