16:18.895 --> 16:20.556
She said she had a class.

16:22.190 --> 16:24.806
Claire, call me
as soon as you get this.

16:24.901 --> 16:26.812
You shouldn't have let her go
without talking to me first.

16:26.903 --> 16:28.279
What was I
supposed to do?

16:28.363 --> 16:31.901
Drag her by her hair,
and lock her
in your closet?

16:34.077 --> 16:36.113
What do you want to do?

16:36.872 --> 16:38.032
We go.

16:38.123 --> 16:39.408
Samuel's escalating
his attacks,

16:39.499 --> 16:41.785
we can't afford to sit around
and wait to see
what he's gonna do next.

16:41.877 --> 16:43.583
LAUREN: You're right,
but you're also emotional.

16:43.670 --> 16:46.537
Look, this Samuel
is a threat,
and notjust to Claire.

16:46.631 --> 16:49.008
You're going with
less than 100% focus.

16:49.092 --> 16:51.629
I can handle this.
You don't have to
worry about me.

16:51.720 --> 16:54.006
That's not
an option anymore.

17:00.228 --> 17:01.684
Let's go.

17:06.526 --> 17:08.437
