17:12.782 --> 17:13.771
Claire?

17:13.867 --> 17:14.902
We need to talk.

17:14.993 --> 17:16.949
What are you doing here?

17:17.787 --> 17:20.449
Your father is coming
for Samuel.

17:21.208 --> 17:24.541
To kill him?
Claire, if Samuel
finds out...

17:24.628 --> 17:26.368
I know. That's why
I came ahead.

17:26.463 --> 17:28.249
l have seen things
like this
go wrong before,

17:28.340 --> 17:31.332
and I don't want
my dad or anyone else
getting hurt.

17:31.426 --> 17:33.758
But we don't have
a lot of time.

17:44.981 --> 17:46.266
Samuel will never
go for it.

17:46.358 --> 17:47.393
He'll never
turn himself in.

17:47.484 --> 17:48.473
We have to try.

17:48.568 --> 17:51.355
Claire, he is not
listening to me,
to anyone.

17:51.446 --> 17:54.779
If your father
is really on his way,
I should get Amanda...

17:54.866 --> 17:57.027
And what, Lydia?
Run away?

17:57.786 --> 17:59.777
Has it come to that?

17:59.996 --> 18:01.987
Can't say I blame you.

18:02.332 --> 18:04.948
What I did to that town,
all those people...

18:05.043 --> 18:08.535
Claire, I had hoped
you'd have a better reason
to come back to us.

18:08.672 --> 18:10.537
How could you do that?

18:10.674 --> 18:13.211
